<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif; background: #FAF5F3; color: #221C1C; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; }
    .header { background: #221C1C; padding: 36px 48px; text-align: center; }
    .header-logo { font-size: 13px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .header-name { font-size: 28px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
    .body { padding: 48px; }
    .intro { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #5a5050; margin-bottom: 32px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    .card { background: #FAF5F3; border-left: 3px solid #9A8585; padding: 28px 32px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .card-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #EAD8D5; }
    .card-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .card-label { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9A8585; }
    .card-value { font-size: 15px; color: #221C1C; text-align: right; }
    .cta { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .cta p { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #9A8585; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .footer { background: #F0E6E2; padding: 24px 48px; text-align: center; }
    .footer p { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #9A8585; line-height: 1.7; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">

    <div class="header">
      <div class="header-logo">Salon d'onglerie · Lorient</div>
      <div class="header-name">Royal Nail</div>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <p class="intro">
        Bonjour <%= @booking.name.split.first %>,<br><br>
        Votre réservation a été annulée. Nous sommes désolés de ne pas pouvoir vous accueillir cette fois-ci.
      </p>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-row">
          <span class="card-label">Prestation annulée</span>
          <span class="card-value"><%= @booking.service %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-row">
          <span class="card-label">Date</span>
          <span class="card-value"><%= @booking.date.strftime('%A %d %B %Y').capitalize %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-row">
          <span class="card-label">Heure</span>
          <span class="card-value"><%= @booking.time_slot %></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cta">
        <p>Pour reprendre rendez-vous ou pour toute question :</p>
        <strong style="font-size:16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">06 27 35 81 88</strong>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #9A8585; line-height: 1.8; text-align: center; padding: 0 48px 32px;">
      Royal Nail · 64 rue Brancion · Paris 15e<br>
      Lundi – Dimanche : 10h – 20h
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>© <%= Date.today.year %> Royal Nail</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
